                            <comment id="12919458" author="stack" created="Sat, 9 Oct 2010 03:46:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is a patch that seems to fix the hang.  We were failing update of meta because location we had for it was bad &amp;#8211; catch the particular IOE type and then wait on update of meta location before proceeding w/ edit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12919459" author="stack" created="Sat, 9 Oct 2010 03:47:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed attached patch to see if it helps up on hudson.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12919537" author="stack" created="Sat, 9 Oct 2010 20:07:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Now this test and the TestTableMapReduce are hanging here:&lt;/p&gt;

